ribed with CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/288845/', '', 'Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Cefepime, Norfloxacin, Metronidazole, Cefuroxime, Secnidazole, Cefixime, Azithromycin, Amikacin, Levofloxacin, More', '', 1767369485);
